{"tid":868599,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【上市未夠一年】雷蛇創辦人押股借錢 股價新低潛水六成","createTime":"2018-10-19T15:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T09:05:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"495ea19bd7efb635bafb6c1a4d87353bf9216a69","tid":868599,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181019/large/1539960220_39cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181019%2Flarge%2F1539960220_39cc.jpg&h=ca858e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雷蛇(1337)上市不足一年，遭創辦人抵押股份！雷蛇剛公佈，大股東Chen Family向瑞銀抵押雷蛇3.59%或3.23億股，作為真誠貸款之抵押品。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，雷蛇創辦人兼主席陳民亮決定押股，屬經家人商討後的私人決定，為家族的財務計劃，對公司的決策沒有影響；而陳民亮作為控股股東及對公司的運作亦不會改變。<br />\n<br />\nChen Family 由陳氏家族信託間接擁有，而陳氏家族信託則由陳民亮設立，並且是信託受益人之一。陳民亮實益持有雷蛇約30.3億股，佔公司已發行股本約33.75%，雷蛇去年11月在新經濟熱潮中上市，挾本港首隻電競股之名，及上市前更獲首富李嘉誠透過維港投資入股，風頭一時無兩，上市首日較招股價升兩成，但隨即打回原形，上市不足一個月，雷蛇已跌穿招股價，其後股價拾級而下，至今仍未能重返招股價，以昨日收市價1.4元，較招股價3.88元跌63.9%，較高位5.49元更大跌74.5%。"},{"pid":"2c8420073edd4eff0b4e7f379499c97a4d4c6c72","tid":868599,"uid":117032,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:32:40.000Z","msg":"等睇大股東卑銀行斬倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659c857568764082a85cd526933923cdbbd982f7","tid":868599,"uid":18395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:51:31.000Z","msg":"真實價格係零"},{"pid":"0aa37e3381b6693a82aaeae92c757d5c7bf70c60","tid":868599,"uid":34005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:04:39.000Z","msg":"頹蛇"},{"pid":"0adc2ac3098a0850fbcd0f9f62aa06fb9fc830cd","tid":868599,"uid":42445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T02:10:48.000Z","msg":"押股同自己公司對賭<br />\n一係賺到笑<br />\n一係輸到喊"},{"pid":"b78d086ae95226dfeb771f0747b635f7840abd3e","tid":868599,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T02:19:20.000Z","msg":"咁缺水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe079f81a9c05292dfd679b6baab8537f914d0e","tid":868599,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T02:21:54.000Z","msg":"奠莖！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb60c02baf2d5e28a30141088abf694958edf9c","tid":868599,"uid":154505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T09:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 產品平平<br />\n食到電莖頭啖湯上市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}